C THE COEFFICIENTS IN PERTST NEED BE GIVEN TO ONLY ABOUT
C ONE PERCENT ACCURACY.  THE ORDER IN WHICH THE GROUPS APPEAR BELOW
C IS..  COEFFICIENTS FOR ORDER NQ - 1, COEFFICIENTS FOR ORDER NQ,
